Text:
Morthergoose, I couldnt find your stuff when I went to look for it the last few days :(

You are a lifesaver for us deployed abroad :)   Please realize that me and my friends really appreciate what you do, in case nobody has ever told you.
From now on I'm bookmarking your page. I type in O&A on the search engine, no new dates show up, so thanks for the upload man.

barrygmu - 

Thanks for all you and your friends do, glad you appreciate the uploads. I may not agree with some of our government's policies but I'll never fault those on the ground for that. Hang in there.....

thanks goose!
